      <div class="image-text">
        <div class="text">
          <h2>Sustainable</h2>
          <p class="para1">Lab-grown diamonds do not require extensive displacement of land nor do they directly destroy ecosystems. When you decide to pick a lab-grown diamond over a mined one, you’re doing your little bit to help conserve and preserve the planet without compromising on your quality of life. Remember, we need to make changes today to ensure that we have a tomorrow to look forward to.</p>
          <h2>Ethical</h2>
          <p>For many years, people were forced to mine for diamonds in war zones to finance civil wars. These diamonds were called blood diamonds. With lab-grown diamonds, you don’t have to worry about blood diamonds at all since the stones are grown in laboratories. This means there’s almost no question of labour being exploited to mine the diamonds or the stones being used for anything other than to decorate pieces of jewellery. When you opt for a lab-grown stone, you get a beautiful piece of jewellery that is completely conflict-free!</p>
        </div>
