      </div>
      <h2>Value for Money</h2>
      <div class="paragraph">
        <div class="left-text">
          <p>Lab-grown diamonds offer you incredibly high value for your money. To obtain a natural diamond, large areas of land need to be mined, which requires not just extensive labour but also time. All of this adds up to make a mined diamond very expensive. On the other hand, lab-grown diamonds are grown in laboratories in just a few weeks with minimal human resources required. This cost-benefit is directly transferred to you, making lab-grown diamonds the better option for your wallet.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="right-text">
          <p>If you opt for a lab-grown diamond over a mined one, you can save a lot on your purchase or choose to upgrade your diamond while on the same budget!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0411/6437/4183/files/Article_page_pic_3_977x486.png?v=1596608488">
